New York Wheel is set to break ground this week on Staten Island . 
  The 630ft observation wheel will be able to carry as many as 1,400 passengers at a time . 
  It will offer stunning views of the Manhattan skyline and other New York boroughs . 
  Dubai started construction a few days ago on a Ferris wheel 60ft higher . 
  The New York Wheel will be completed in early 2017 and cost $25 to $30 for a 38-minute ride . 
 